e slot\n\nWrapping the column name with SqlUtils.quote() turns the whole user-\nsupplied string into a single Postgres identifier, which Postgres\nrejects at parse time when it doesn't exist — preventing the inner\nSQL from being evaluated. This is exactly the defense already in\nplace for the parallel sink in getCriteriaSqlClause (line 369).\n\nCompanion regression tests in SqlViewControllerIntegrationTest cover\nboth known exploitation techniques (UNION-based and CAST/error-based)\nand demonstrate the leak on the unfixed code.\n\nAI Assisted\n\nRefs GHSA-pwmg-mvjw-4m23","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"netroms@gmail.com"},"id":"e860b8162883da6d1b565297085482a85cf4db7f","tree_id":"5963c4af260ee22e9682ce04a8f92bc6fac51b11","timestamp":"2026-06-09T10:26:17Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. 